features: [Durable & Hand-woven] Our rope hanging plant extenders are hand-woven from multiple strands of cotton rope. Each rope for hanging plants is added with a wooden ring, more solid and durable, wear-resistant, not easy to break, not deformed, with good toughness, washable, strong bearing capacity, which can be used for a long time and save a lot of space for your home.

[Package Contents] You will receive a pack of 6 macrame plant hanger extenders, which is enough to meet your needs for using and replacing in multiple flower pots. You can also share with friends and relatives to experience the joy of displaying plants together.

[Connectable Hanger Extender] Each hanging plant rope extension is 11.8 inches in length, you can string these extenders for plant pot holder according to the actual needs, connect them to the length you want, very easy to use, 6 ropes strung together for a total length of 60 inches, long enough for multiple planters.

[Bohemian Style] This hanging rope for plants indoor with woven design, beautiful and simple shape, exquisite workmanship, with a flower pot, very decorative, is a wonderful bohemian style home decor, suitable for indoor and outdoor, so that your living room, balcony, courtyard, etc. to add more elegance.

[Perfect Gift Choice] Our long plant hanger is perfect for plant lovers to hang their beloved plants safely and display them anywhere for better appreciation, it definitely caters to their practical needs and is a practical and beautiful gift.
